title: Console Divinity: Original Sin gets a release date
text:
Console Divinity: Original Sin gets a release date 
Published By: Eurogamer.net - Today 
Larian Studios has told Eurogamer the Enhanced Edition of Divinity: Original Sin, AKA the console version, will be released 27th October 201...
